sub_title: Teacher with a passion for academic skills and chemistry, specialised in spectroscopy. Great organisational skills.
summary:
Highly skilled analytical chemist with a strong sense of responsibility, critical eye and excellent teaching capabilities. I am at my best in a stimulating environment where I can apply my theoretical knowledge and practical experience to help students or researchers get the best out of themselves. 

Experienced in vibrational spectroscopy (IR, Raman) and microscopy for environmental and biomedical applications
